{"id": "1322423797818855425", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "一般我的認知提到自選都是在說限定自選活動\n你所謂的自選是用輪轉這個普池用 我們理解的有差別", "timestamp": "2024-12-28T04:40:02.846000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
